By":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb432b48b8b74a2bb586b6f7fe33b4c975cacec","tid":1496781,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心<br />\nd相仲會改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9d82f66d1dc96df3761e20e06977f06b386fa1","tid":1496781,"uid":281584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:14:19.000Z","msg":"真正對香港不利嘅外國觀點<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zMm_7jb3Cds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzMm_7jb3Cds&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=12f36e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zMm_7jb3Cds</a><br />\n有好多人認為香港人支持西方殖民主義<br />\n條友偷換概念<br />\n仲要用大陸官媒嘅說法去描述<br />\n對於陰謀論者或者唔鐘意傳統西方媒體嘅外國人嚟講係啱聽<br />\n總有西方左膠認為中國好L慘,比西方蝦,自己想做英雄或成為眾人皆醉我獨醒<br />\n事實係中國殖民香港,破壞英國留下嘅民主法治自由<br />\n有冇外國yuotuber可以幫我地反駁佢"},{"pid":"b6e5474ef9cd42067e9bcf2aeadf702dcd3cd670","tid":1496781,"uid":41364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a0a5eb13f3e8852402cdf5662695a9205be408","tid":1496781,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n823 人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;823 23:59死線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494948\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494948</a><br />\n<br />\n824 朝早7點機場<br />\n<br />\n824 晏晝1點觀塘<br />\n<br />\n825 荃葵青<br />\n <br />\n831 中聯辦<br />\n<br />